quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,Agar hum inpar reham karein aur woh takleef jis mein aaj kal yeh mubtila hain door kardein to yeh apni sarkashi mein bilkul hi behak jayenge
  23,76,"Inka haal to yeh hai ke humne unhein takleef mein mubtila kiya, phir bhi yeh apne Rubb ke aagey na jhuke aur na aajizi (humble)ikhtiyar karte hain"
  23,77,Albatta jab naubat yahan tak pahunch jayegi ke hum inpar sakht azaab ka darwaza khol denge to yakayak tum dekhoge ke us halat mein ye har khair se mayous hain
  23,78,"Woh Allah hi to hai jisne tumhein sunney aur dekhne ki quwwatein di aur sochne ko dil diye , magar tum log kam hi shukarguzar hotey ho"
  23,79,"Wahi hai jisne tumhein zameen mein phaylaya, aur usi ki taraf tum sametay jaogey"
  23,80,"Wahi zindagi bakashta hai aur wahi maut deta hai, gardish e layl (raat) o nahar (din) usi ke qabze qudrat mein hai. Kya tumhari samajh mein yeh baat nahin aati"
  23,81,Magar yeh log wahi kuch kehte hain jo unke peshraw (forefathers) keh chuke hain
  23,82,Yeh kehte hain “kya jab hum marr kar mitti ho jayenge aur haddiyon ka panjar ban kar reh jayenge to humko phir zinda karke uthaya jayega
  23,83,Humne bhi yeh wadey bahut sunay hain aur humse pehle hamare baap dada bhi suntey rahey hain. Yeh mehaz afasana haye pareena hain(ancient tales)”
  23,84,"Insey kaho, batao agar tum jaante ho, ke yeh zameen aur iski saari aabaadi kiski hai"
  23,85,"Yeh zaroor kahenge ke Allah ki, kaho phir tum hosh mein kyun nahin aatey"
  23,86,"Insey pucho, saato (seven) aasmaano aur arsh-e-azeem ka maalik kaun hai"
  23,87,"Yeh zaroor kahenge Allah, kaho phir tum darte kyun nahin"
  23,88,"Insey kaho, batao agar tum jaante ho ke har cheez par iqtedaar kiska hai? Aur kaun hai woh jo panaah deta hai aur uske muqable mein koi panaah nahin de sakta"
  23,89,"Yeh zaroor kahenge ke yeh baat to Allah hi keliye hai. Kaho, phir kahan se tumko dhoka lagta hai"
  23,90,"Jo amr e haqq hai woh hum inke saamne le aaye hain, aur koi shakk nahin ke yeh log jhotey hain"
  23,91,"Allah ne kisi ko apni aulaad nahin banaya hai aur koi dusra khuda uske saath nahin hai. Agar aisa hota to har khuda apni khalq ko lekar alag ho jaata, aur phir woh ek dusre par chadh daudte.Paak hai Allah un baaton se jo yeh log banate hain"
  23,92,"Khule aur chupe ka jaanne wala, woh baalatar hai us shirk se jo yeh log tajweez kar rahey hain"
  23,93,"(Aey Muhammad) dua karo ke “parwardigar, jis azaab ki inko dhamki di jaa rahi hai woh agar meri maujoodgi mein tu laye"
  23,94,"To aey mere Rubb, mujhey in zaalim logon mein shamil na kijiyo”"
  23,95,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke hum tumhari aankhon ke saamne hi woh cheez le aane ki poori qudrat rakhte hain jiski dhamki hum unhein de rahey hain
  23,96,"(Aey Nabi), burayi ko is tareeqe se dafa karo jo behtareen ho jo kuch baatein woh tumpar banate hain woh humein khoob maloom hai"
  23,97,"Aur dua karo ke “parwardigar, main shayateen ki uksahaton(waswason) se teri panaah maangta hoon"
  23,98,"Balke aey mere Rubb, main to issey bhi teri panaah maanga hoon ke woh mere paas aayein”"
  23,99,"(yeh log apni karni se baaz na aayenge) yahan tak ke jab in mein se kisi ko maut aa jayegi to kehna shuru kardega ke “Aey mere Rubb, mujhey usi duniya mein wapas bhej dijiye jisey main chodh aaya hoon"
  23,100,"Umeed hai ke ab main neik amal karunga”. Hargiz nahin, yeh to bas ek baat hai jo woh bakk raha hai. Ab in sab (marne waalon) ke peechey ek barzakh (barrier) hayal hai dusri zindagi ke din tak"
  23,101,"Phir junhi ke Sur (trumphet) phoonk diya gaya, unke darmiyan phir koi rishta na rahega aur na woh ek dusre ko puchenge"
  23,102,Us waqt jinke padle (scales) bhari hongey wahi falaah payenge
  23,103,Aur jinke padle (scales) halke honge wahi log hongey jinhon ne apne aap ko ghatay mein daal liya. Woh jahannum mein hamesha rahenge
  23,104,Aag unke chehron ki khaal chaat jayegi aur unke jabde (jaws) bahar nikal aayenge
  23,105,“kya tum wahi log nahin ho ke meri aayat tumhein sunayi jati thi to tum unhein jhutlate thay?”
  23,106,"Woh kahenge “aey hamare Rubb, hamari badbakhti hum par chaa gayi thi, hum waqayi gumraah log thay"
  23,107,"Aey parwardigar, ab humein yahan se nikaal de phir hum aisa kasoor karein to zaalim hongey”"
  23,108,"Allah taala jawab dega “ door ho mere saamne se, padey raho isi mein aur mujhse baat na karo"
  23,109,"Tum wahi log to ho ke mere kuch banday jab kehte thay ke aye hamare parwardigar, hum iman laye, humein maaf karde, humpar reham kar, tu sab raheemon se accha raheem hai"
  23,110,"To tumne unka mazaaq bana liye, yahan tak ke unki zidd ne tumhein yeh bhi bhula diya ke main bhi koi hoon, aur tum unpar haste rahey"
  23,111,Aaj unke us sabr ka maine yeh phal diya hai ke wahi kamiyaab hain”
  23,112,"Phir Allah taala unse puchega “batao,zameen mein tum kitne saal rahey?”"
  23,113,"Woh kahenge “ ek din ya din ka bhi kuch hissa hum wahan thehre hain, shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye”"
  23,114,"Irshad hoga “ thodi hi dair thehre ho na, kaash tumne yeh us waqt jana hota"
  23,115,Kya tumne yeh samajh rakkha tha ke humne tumhein fizul(bekar) hi paida kiya hai aur tumhein hamari taraf kabhi palatna hi nahin hai?”
  23,116,"Pas baala o bartar hai Allah , baadshah e haqiqi, koi khuda uske siwa nahin, maalik hai arsh e buzurg ka"
  23,117,"Aur jo koi Allah ke saath kisi aur maabood ko pukare, jiske liye uske paas koi daleel nahin, to uska hisaab uske Rubb ke paas hai. Aisey kafir kabhi falaah nahin paa sakte"
  23,118,"(Aey Muhammad) kaho, “Mere Rubb darguzar farma, aur reham kar, aur tu sab raheemon se accha raheem hai”"